<!-- 소액수의 실무흐름도 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-indigo-500">account_tree</span>
      소액수의 실무흐름도
    </h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1">추정가격 기준 소액수의계약 진행 절차</p>
  </div>

  <div class="p-6">
    <!-- 사전단계 안내 -->
    <div class="mb-6 p-3 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl text-sm text-amber-800 flex items-start gap-2">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-500 mt-0.5" style="font-size:18px">info</span>
      <span>사업기본계획 수립 및 예산확보 완료 후의 절차입니다. 사전준비 단계는 <a href="<%= topic_path('private-contract') %>" class="text-amber-700 underline font-semibold hover:text-amber-900">수의계약 실무흐름도</a>를 참고하세요.</span>
    </div>

    <!-- 처리 절차 -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <!-- Step 1: indigo -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-indigo-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-800 mb-2">추정가격 산정
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 text-xs font-normal rounded-full"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:12px">edit_document</span>공문생산</span>
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 예정가격 작성 기준에 따라 <strong class="text-indigo-700">추정가격 산정</strong></li>
            <li>• 소액수의 기준 금액 이하 여부 확인</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-indigo-700">동일 품목 분할 계약 금지</strong> 확인</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="<%= budget_estimator_path %>" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white hover:bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg border border-indigo-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md active:shadow-inner active:bg-indigo-100 transition-all">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">calculate</span>
              소요예산 추정
            </a>
            <a href="<%= contract_method_path %>" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white hover:bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg border border-indigo-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md active:shadow-inner active:bg-indigo-100 transition-all">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">swap_horiz</span>
              계약방식 결정
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: blue -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-blue-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">견적 방법 결정</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 border border-blue-300 rounded-lg p-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-700">2인 이상 견적</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 mt-1">2천만원 초과 ~ 기준금액 이하</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-800 mt-1 font-medium">→ <strong class="text-blue-700">나라장터 의무</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-3">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-700">1인 견적 가능</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 mt-1">2천만원 이하</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-800 mt-1 font-medium">→ 나라장터 불필요</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: violet -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-violet-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-violet-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-violet-800 mb-2">견적서 징구
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 text-xs font-normal rounded-full"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:12px">computer</span>시스템</span>
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">2인 견적:</strong> 나라장터(G2B)·학교장터에 견적 공고</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">1인 견적:</strong> 업체에 직접 견적 요청</li>
            <li>• 견적서 접수 및 비교 검토</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">최저가 견적 업체 선정</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: amber -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-amber-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">계약 체결
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 text-xs font-normal rounded-full"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:12px">edit_document</span>공문생산</span>
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 계약서 작성 (<strong class="text-amber-700">소액은 청구서로 갈음 가능</strong>)</li>
            <li>• 계약보증금 납부 (<strong class="text-amber-700">면제 가능</strong>)</li>
            <li>• 계약 체결 및 통지</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="<%= contract_documents_path %>" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 bg-white hover:bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg border border-amber-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md active:shadow-inner active:bg-amber-100 transition-all">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">description</span>
              계약서류 생성
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5: green -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-green-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">이행 및 대금 지급
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 text-xs font-normal rounded-full"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:12px">edit_document</span>공문생산</span>
          </h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 계약 이행 및 <strong class="text-green-700">검수</strong></li>
            <li>• 대금 청구서 접수</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-green-700">대금 지급 완료</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 참고 안내 (접히는 섹션) -->
    <details open class="mt-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
      <summary class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-500">info</span>
        <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700">참고 안내</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 ml-auto">기준금액 · 나라장터 의무 · 주의사항</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-4 space-y-4">
        <!-- 소액수의 기준 금액 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-500">info</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">소액수의 기준 금액 <span class="text-xs font-normal bg-slate-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full ml-2">현행</span></h4>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
                  <span class="font-medium text-slate-700">공사</span>
                  <p class="text-slate-600">추정가격 <strong>8천만원 이하</strong></p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3">
                  <span class="font-medium text-slate-700">물품·용역</span>
                  <p class="text-slate-600">추정가격 <strong>5천만원 이하</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 나라장터 의무 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <span class="text-sm text-slate-700">📌 <strong>지방계약법 시행령 제30조②:</strong> 2인 이상 견적 시 지정정보처리장치(나라장터) 의무 이용</span>
        </div>

        <!-- 주의사항 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400">warning</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">주의사항</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
                <li>• 동일 품목을 분할하여 소액수의 기준에 맞추는 것은 <strong>위법</strong></li>
                <li>• 특정 업체 지정을 위한 규격 조작 금지</li>
                <li>• 견적서는 반드시 원본 징구 (이메일, 팩스 가능)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>
